agt-opencode — AGT runtime governance for OpenCode
==================================================

This project is an independent, personal integration. It is not affiliated
with, endorsed by, or supported by Microsoft, SST, or the OpenCode project.

It packages and adapts components of Microsoft's Agent Governance Toolkit
(AGT) so they run as an OpenCode plugin.

